{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_04_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 2話 人を笑顔に出来る力",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんを、目指さなくていい……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I really not have to aim for Mana-chan…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣と麻奈は違う。それに芽衣はもう立派なアイドルだ\n麻奈を目指すよりも、参考にする、と考えたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei and Mana are different. Besides‚ Mei is already a splendid idol.\nInstead of aiming for Mana‚ how about using her as a reference?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 15.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんを目指すんじゃなくて、参考にする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not aiming to be like Mana-chan‚ but using her as a reference…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 21.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "新しいことにチャレンジするのはとてもいいと思う\nだから、意識の仕方をちょっと変えてみたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's great to challenge new things.\nSo‚ how about changing your mindset a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9341570537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、いろいろ試すのは大丈夫なんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ it's okay to try various things‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "むむむ……それなら、やっぱりすずにゃんと二人で\nアメリカ修行に行った方がいいかなー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… In that case‚ maybe it's better for me and Suzu-nyan\nto go for training in the U.S~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それはさすがに心配だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'm a bit worried about that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 47.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、芽衣が麻奈のことをこんなに考えて\n成長しようと頑張ってくれてるのは嬉しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm happy that Mei think so much about Mana\nand are making an effort to grow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 53.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "えへへー、照れるなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ you're making me blush.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 57.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ、新しいチャレンジが出来る\nお仕事ってないかなー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey‚ is there any\nnew job opportunity~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "新しい……か。そういえば、ダンススクールからの\n依頼がちょうど今日きたところだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something new… Oh‚ right‚ there was an offer\nfrom a dance school that came today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 70.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "ダンススクール？　何をするお仕事なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A dance school? What kind of job is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 74.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "星見市のダンススクールなんだが、生徒の子供達が\n月スト……特に芽衣のダンスが好きらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a dance school in Hoshimi City‚ and the children there\nlove Moon Tempest‚ especially your dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "講師の方とは知り合いでな、良かったら子供達と\n話をしたり、ダンスを教えてほしいってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I happen to know the instructor‚ so if you're interested‚\nyou can talk to the kids and teach them some dance moves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 89.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "わー、楽しそう！　やるやる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ that sounds fun! I'm in‚ I'm in!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 94.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "即答だな。よし、じゃあ先方に伝えておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was a quick response. Alright‚ I'll let them know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "楽しみだなー。最近お仕事でもライブでも\nあんまり星見市に行けてなかったしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm looking forward to it. Lately‚ I haven't been able to go to\nHoshimi City much for work or live performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 108.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "参考に聞きたいんだけど、麻奈ちゃんって\n子供達にはどんな感じだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to ask for your reference.\nHow was Mana-chan with the kids?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 114.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "年齢なんて関係なく誰とでもすぐに仲良くなれたよ\nそういう意味では芽衣と近いかもしれないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Age doesn't matter‚ she easily becomes friends with anyone.\nIn that sense‚ she's similar to you‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "星見まつりのライブが終わった後なんか\nファンの女の子と喋った！　って楽しそうに言ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the Hoshimi Festival live‚ she was excitedly talking\nabout having a conversation with a fan girl.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 130.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、麻奈ちゃんはどこにいても\n誰といても麻奈ちゃんなんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ no matter where she is‚\nshe's Mana-chan to everyone she's with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 138.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "やっほー！　月ストの芽衣だよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yaho! It's Mei from Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.666666700007,
          "startTime": 143
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "わわっ、熱烈な歓迎！　えへへー、嬉しいな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ such a warm welcome! Hehe‚ I'm so happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "今日はみんなといーっぱいお話ししちゃうよー\nなんでも聞いてね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I'm going to talk a lot with everyone.\nAsk me anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_04_02-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "それで、お話が終わったら～……\n芽衣と一緒に、月ストの曲で踊ってみよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And after we finish talking…\nLet's dance to a Moon Tempest song together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8599.999999999995,
          "startTime": 167.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
